        "description": "Select channels (comma-separated): Email, WhatsApp, SMS, Push Notification, Google Ads, Meta Ads, TikTok Ads, Twitter/X Ads, Reddit Ads, LinkedIn Ads, Trade Show, TV, Radio, Telecalling, Outdoor, Print, Event, Omni-Channel"
    },
